metadata.name: RED TEAR DROPS
metadata.description:
21th of February, the anniversary of my father's death. 
I left home to go to my father's grave. A sudden fog appeared, the visibility dramatically reduced and traffic was about to stop. Due to the lack of driving safety, I decided to go back and take a tea break. At that time, I saw the woman in the red shawl with a coffee mug in her hand, she was feeding the birds. It was a movie like scene. I took out my camera and shoot using the flash. I named the photo "Red Tear Drops" in accordance with the meaning of the day.

Edition - 1/1

Location - Kadikoy / Istanbul / Turkey 

Dimension - 4608x3456
